                <ol class="rotation-steps">
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Cast Frozen Orb continuously</strong> &mdash; Your primary action. Launch Frozen Orbs into packs to generate massive explosions that freeze everything. Esu's Heirloom reduces cooldown on crits.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Ice Blades for passive damage</strong> &mdash; Keep Ice Blades active for automated attacks that apply Vulnerable and trigger Aspect of Control. Recast whenever available.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Frost Nova for instant freeze</strong> &mdash; Use Frost Nova when enemies get too close or when you need immediate crowd control. Low cooldown allows frequent defensive resets.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Ice Armor for barriers</strong> &mdash; Maintain Ice Armor for constant barrier uptime. Provides both damage reduction and mana regeneration for sustained casting.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Teleport for repositioning</strong> &mdash; Use Teleport to escape danger, reposition for better Frozen Orb angles, or trigger Bounding Conduit for bonus movement speed.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="rotation-step">
                        <p><strong>Deep Freeze for emergencies</strong> &mdash; Pop Deep Freeze when overwhelmed or surrounded. The immunity window allows you to reset combat and wait for cooldowns to come back up.</p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
